REG_CTRL0 
7          - multy fonts
 654       - video mode
    32     - font bits
      10   - scale

multy fonts - for mode 8 x 8, 8 x 16 and 16 x 16, enable diferent font for 1/3 lines

video mode -
    000 - 8 x 8
    001 - 8 x 8 multy color, diferent color for each line
    010 - 8 x 16
    011 - 8 x 16 multy color
    100 - 16 x 16
    101 - 16 x 32
    110 - 32 x 32
    111 - graph mode

font bits - 
    00 - 1 bit 
    01 - 2 bits
    10 - 4 bits
    11 - none (1 bits now, may be 8 bits future)

scale - 
    00 - 1x
    01 - 2x for X and Y
    10 - 4x
    11 - none (1x now)
